          "History"
        ],
        "dom_section_identifier": "rch-pic-acute-abdominal-pain-children-2024-section-0009",
        "position": 8,
        "paragraph_or_text_span": "Pain characteristics and associated symptoms (see Additional notes for causes associated with these pain characteristics) Systemic symptoms: fever, lethargy, irritability, anorexia, weight loss Dietary history Stool eg diarrhoea, constipation, blood , mucus Vomiting eg bilious , blood Urinary symptoms eg dysuria, polyuria, polydipsia Menstrual and sexual history in adolescents Psychosocial history",
        "normalized_span_fingerprint": "4a2c4d912e023fa95515a57937b413f453076503f94508a2de9430ab4c7194c6",
        "page_start": null,
        "page_end": null,
        "section_id": "rch-pic-acute-abdominal-pain-children-2024-section-0009"
      }
